channel.title: Loading Maps :(
channel.description: I added the new Christmas costume to my client, compiled, then ran my client. My client was saying "Loading maps 75%" for at least 3 minutes, so I went back deleted the models, removed the costume from my class8.java, and just removed everything about it from the client and server, and it's still saying "Loading maps 75%"... No errors are coming up on the client of server run. So what could be causing this?... Please help.
